headline: Dandelion Energy and Lennar Announce One of the Largest Residential Geothermal Deployments in US History
summary: Dandelion Energy, the nation's leading home geothermal heating and cooling company, today announced they are partnering with Lennar Corporation (NYSE: LEN and LEN. B), one of the nation's leading homebuilders, on one of the most significant residential geothermal heat pump deployments in US history.
